### Overview

It would be really nice if there is an overload for the StringPool.GetOrAdd method which accepts a custom InterpolatedStringHandler. This InterpolatedStringHandler would create a ReadOnlySpan<char>and use this to get the string from the pool without any string allocation (if available in the pool). 


### API breakdown

